casebody.data:
Carlton ROBINSON, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 18-6915. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 7, 2019.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied. Justice SOTOMAYOR, with whom Justice GINSBURG joins, dissenting from the denial of certiorari: I dissent for the reasons set out in *854Brown v. United States, 586 U.S. ----, 139 S.Ct. 624, 202 L.Ed.2d 450 (2018) (Sotomayor, J., dissenting).
